---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="蒙太奇字幕社区 - 赋能字幕生态">
	<section class="relative pt-32 pb-20 overflow-hidden">
		<div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full h-full bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_center,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-yellow-400/10 via-transparent to-transparent -z-10"></div>
		
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
			<h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black tracking-tighter mb-8 animate-fade-in">
				字幕即<span class="text-yellow-400">纽带</span>
			</h1>
			<p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed mb-12">
				我们不仅是在翻译台词，更是在构建一个透明、专业且由技术驱动的跨语言交流生态系统。
			</p>
			<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
				<a href="/zh-hans/tools" class="bg-yellow-400 text-black px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-bold text-lg hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(250,204,21,0.5)] transition-all">
					探索开源工具库
				</a>
				<a href="#mission" class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-bold text-lg hover:bg-white/10 transition">
					查看案例研究
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section id="mission" class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
		<div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-zinc-900 border border-white/5 hover:border-yellow-400/50 transition">
			<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-yellow-400/10 text-yellow-400 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl mb-6 text-2xl">🛠️</div>
			<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">开源工具领导者</h3>
			<p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">开发并维护从 AI 自动轴到术语库同步的全链路工具，降低专业字幕制作的门槛。</p>
		</div>
		<div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-zinc-900 border border-white/5 hover:border-yellow-400/50 transition">
			<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-yellow-400/10 text-yellow-400 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl mb-6 text-2xl">🧠</div>
			<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">学术化翻译思维</h3>
			<p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">通过 Blog 和 Wiki 沉淀翻译中的文化考据与逻辑拆解，实现真正的翻译透明化。</p>
		</div>
		<div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-zinc-900 border border-white/5 hover:border-yellow-400/50 transition">
			<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-yellow-400/10 text-yellow-400 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl mb-6 text-2xl">👥</div>
			<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">去中心化社区</h3>
			<p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">基于 GitHub 协作，尊重每一位贡献者的劳动，让每份热爱都能在个人页面熠熠生辉。</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-20 border-y border-white/5 bg-zinc-950">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 flex flex-wrap justify-around gap-12">
			<div class="text-center">
				<div class="text-5xl font-black text-white mb-2">15+</div>
				<div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-yellow-400 font-bold">开源项目</div>
			</div>
			<div class="text-center">
				<div class="text-5xl font-black text-white mb-2">400+</div>
				<div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-yellow-400 font-bold">贡献者</div>
			</div>
			<div class="text-center">
				<div class="text-5xl font-black text-white mb-2">0</div>
				<div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-yellow-400 font-bold">商业侵权</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	@keyframes fade-in {
		from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
		to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
	}
	.animate-fade-in {
		animation: fade-in 1s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
	}
</style>